title: Libby Schaaf
added: In March of 2021, Mayor Libby Schaaf announced that non-white, low-income residents of Oakland, CA would be entitled to collect a $500 "guaranteed income" payment for 18 month.

<ref>{{cite web |title=Oakland will give low-income families of color $500 per month, no strings attached | url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/24/us/oakland-low-income-bipoc-guaranteed-income-trnd/index.html | access-date=25 March 2021}}</ref>
